She slept in a deep sleep. She dreamed of fighting the other pred 
group and how she tried escape the vents before the cannons shot at 
her.  She mumbled in her sleep, "Quickstrike" She dreamed of getting 
back into the ships and changing sides.  She saw her commander 
Quickstrike and Black Aracnia.  She was fighing with them and against 
them at the same time.  She saw the Dinobots comming after her.  She 
tried to run but couldn't move.  She looked and saw the dinobots 
charge into the bridge and fire on Quickstrike, Black Aracnia, 
Paralysis and herself.  She tried to fire her gun, but all was moving 
in slow motion.  She saw the computer get blown up and she jumped up 
onto the console or what was left of it. She then saw missles aimed 
at her and hit her.  She felt herself fall and land on the floor.  
She mumbled in her sleep,"Sorry commander,I'm sorry"

She drifted in and out of the reoccuring dreams, mumbling and 
whispereing in her sleep.
